Uses of Package
org.wattdepot.datamodel

  • Packages that use org.wattdepot.datamodel 
    Package Description
    org.wattdepot.client
    Various WattDepot clients.
    org.wattdepot.client.restlet
    Restlet implementations of WattDepot clients.
    org.wattdepot.client.restlet.collector
    Collectors are the processes that query Sensors, produce Measurements and send the Measurements to the WattDepot Server.
    org.wattdepot.datamodel
    Provides classes relevant to any WattDepot data model.
    org.wattdepot.restlet
    Provides classes and interfaces relevant to the REST/HTTP contract between the clients and the server.
    org.wattdepot.server
    Server classes.
    org.wattdepot.server.depository.impl.hibernate
    Provides Hibernate implementation of WattDepot.
    org.wattdepot.server.restlet
    Provides classes for the Restlet ServerResources.
    org.wattdepot.util
    Utility classes for WattDepot.
